I"<h1 id="pycharm-matplotlib-in-interactive-mode">Pycharm matplotlib in interactive mode</h1>
<h2 id="solution">Solution:</h2>
<pre><code class="language-python3">import matplotlib as mpl
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
mpl.use('macosx')

plt.plot(range(10))
</code></pre>
<ul>
  <li>or</li>
</ul>

<pre><code>Disable Settings | Tools | Python Scientific | Show plots in tool window.
</code></pre>

